OL,3,CTax on large companies could raise
OL,4,Cfunds for Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FA new tax hike on Jersey's largest
OL,7,Fmultinational companies could see #67m
OL,8,Fspent on financing the island's
OL,9,Fhospital over a three year period.
OL,11,FThe Pillar Two tax scheme would apply
OL,12,Fa 15% minimum tax rate for companies
OL,13,Fwith global annual profits of more
OL,14,Fthan #640m.
OL,16,FJersey's government has published its
OL,17,Flegislation which estimates the tax
OL,18,Fwill raise #52m annually.
