OL,3,CTax on large companies could raise
OL,4,Cfunds for Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FGuernsey has previously estimated they
OL,7,Fcould raise more than #30m a year
OL,8,Fusing the same system.
OL,10,FAround 130 jurisdictions, including
OL,11,FJersey and Guernsey, want to introduce
OL,12,Fthe tax to crack down on 'profit
OL,13,Fshifting'.
OL,15,FThis is where major companies move
OL,16,Ftheir money to lower tax jurisdictions
OL,17,Fto avoid higher taxes.
