OL,3,CTax on large companies could raise
OL,4,Cfunds for Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FAssistant Treasury Minister Ian Gorst
OL,7,Fsays the tax would affect around 5% of
OL,8,Fall Jersey-based corporations -
OL,9,Fapproximately 1,400 companies overall.
OL,11,FHe explained: "We are proposing that
OL,12,Fwe'll use (the tax) to finance the
OL,13,Fhospital, but equally, we need to
OL,14,Fensure that we remain competitive and
OL,15,Fthere will be allocating money to do
OL,16,Fthat as well."
OL,18,FThe government's budget has estimated
OL,19,Fwhat money raised between 2026-2028
OL,20,Fcan go towards:
