OL,3,CTax on large companies could raise
OL,4,Cfunds for Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FHowever, Senior Investment Director,
OL,7,FBen Shenton, has concerns that taxing
OL,8,Fcorporations will not be in Jersey's
OL,9,Fbest interests.
OL,11,FMr Shenton stated: "If you're going to
OL,12,Fbe paying 15% tax in Jersey - and
OL,13,Fpaying a lot more as we're an
OL,14,Fexpensive island for professional
OL,15,Fservices - it erodes the advantages of
OL,16,Fbeing a tax haven.
