OL,3,CTax on large companies could raise
OL,4,Cfunds for Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,F"In the very short term, it's great as
OL,7,Fwe're going to get money for the new
OL,8,Fhospital, but it's a bit like someone
OL,9,Fbringing you a gift before they set
OL,10,Ffire to your house.
OL,12,F"The implications could be quite dire
OL,13,Fand the government has to start
OL,14,Fthinking longer-term, rather than
OL,15,Fgrabbing the money."
OL,17,FHowever, Deputy Gorst said those who
OL,18,Ffear corporations will be put off
OL,19,Fcoming to Jersey have a "lack of
OL,20,Funderstanding" of how the tax system
OL,21,Fis being developed.
