OL,3,CTax on large companies could raise
OL,4,Cfunds for Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FDeputy Gorst added: "The bedrock of
OL,7,FJersey's economy is financial services
OL,8,Fand we need to do everything we can to
OL,9,Fensure that it remains firm, strong,
OL,10,Fand secure.
OL,12,F"The whole purpose is those in-scope
OL,13,Fcompanies cannot avoid paying tax on
OL,14,Ftheir profits
OL,16,F"So the choice is do companies pay
OL,17,Ftheir tax on Jersey profits in Jersey,
OL,18,Ftherefore benefiting islanders, or do
OL,19,Fthey pay those profits in another
OL,20,Fcountry?"
